<Content_wSideColumn ID="x28929" Name="Job Search Tools" Layout="byuidefault.xsl"><Title type="string" label="Title" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="true">Job Search Tools</Title><Abstract type="string" label="Abstract" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="true">A collection of several tools and resources to help students search for employment.</Abstract><xPower Type="GroupStart" GroupStart="" Name="SideColumn" label="L/R Column" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="false"><MoveLeft type="boolean" label="Toggle column right or left (right is default)" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false">false</MoveLeft><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="ImageComponent" label="Image Component" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="LeftColumnImageComponent"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="TextComponent" label="Text Component" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="ColumnTextComponent"/><fbookTop type="boolean" label="Put facebook at top of page" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false">false</fbookTop><fbookStatus type="string" label="Facebook ID#" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false"></fbookStatus><fbookToken type="string" label="Access_Token" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false"></fbookToken><fbookDisplayed type="string" label="Number of facebook messages to display" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false">1</fbookDisplayed></xPower><BodyCopy type="dhtml" label="Body Copy" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false"><![CDATA[<h2>Career Navigator</h2>
<p>A database designed to assist students in their search for job and internship opportunities.&nbsp; Along with jobs and internships, companies post interview and campus visit schedules for students to sign up.</p>
<p><a href="x94514.xml" title="Jobs by College">See list of jobs by college</a><a href="https://byui-csm.symplicity.com/students" title="Career Navigator" target="_blank"><br />Search using Career Navigator</a></p>
<hr />
<h2>Expeditions</h2>
<p>Expeditions give students opportunities to explore their industry in the cities where they are interested in working. Applications are submitted through career navigator.</p>
<p><a href="x89584.xml" title="Expeditions">Learn about expeditions</a></p>
<hr />
<h2>Alumni Office</h2>
<p>A resource for BYU-Idaho students and graduates to connect with alumni around the world. Great for finding a mentor, learning about job opportunities and seeking out career advice.<br /><a href="http://www.byuiconnect.com" title="BYU-Idaho Connect"><br />Connect with an Alumnus</a></p>
<hr />
<h2>LDS Jobs Website</h2>
<p>A website run by the Church designed to help job seekers make and reach career goals. Register and create a profile to be seen by potential employers. Your bishop and other leaders, along with the LDS Jobs staff, will be there to help.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.LDSJobs.org" target="_blank">LDSJobs Website</a></p>
<hr />
<h2>Glassdoor</h2>
<p>Glassdoor is a free jobs and career community that offers the world an inside look at jobs and companies.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.glassdoor.com/index.htm" title="Go to Glassdoor.com"><img alt="&rdquo;Glassdoor.com&rdquo;" height="60" src="Images/advising/careerservices/Student's%20Acc%20GLD.com%20dark.png" title="Go to Glassdoor.com" width="170" /></a></p>
<hr />
<h2>LDS Employment Centers (Off-Campus)<strong><br /></strong></h2>
<p>Centers assist people to discover, develop and market their individual skills.<br /><br /><a href="https://www.ldsjobs.org/ers/ct/articles/what-to-expect-when-visiting-an-employment-center?lang=eng" title="ERS Webpage" target="_blank">Find Center Info</a></p>
<hr />
<h2>Other Job/Career Search Websites</h2>
<p>The following services are free to job seekers:</p>
<p><a href="http://www.jobbankinfo.org/" title="Job Bank" target="_blank">America's Job Bank</a><br /><a href="http://www.internshipprograms.com" title="Internship Programs" target="_blank">Internship Programs</a><br /><a href="http://monster.com" title="Monster.com">Monster</a><br /><a href="http://www.careermag.com/" title="Career Mag" target="_blank">Career Magazine</a><br /><a href="http://www.careerbuilder.com/" title="Career Builder" target="_blank">Career Builder </a><br /><a href="http://www.careercity.com/" title="Career City" target="_blank">True Careers</a><a href="http://www.jobweb.org/" title="NACE Job Web" target="_blank"> </a><br /><a href="http://www.indeed.com" title="Indeed.com" target="_blank">Indeed </a><br /><a href="http://jobs.shrm.org/home/index.cfm?site_id=1612" title="SHRM" target="_blank">Society of Human Resources Management<br /></a><a href="http://www.idsba.org/node/278" title="Idaho School Boards Association Job Center">Idaho School Boards Association (ISBA)&nbsp;Job Center</a></p>
